ory?  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 4aErster Weltkrieg. 4aHistorisches Gedächtnis. 4aKollektives Gedächtnis. 4aRassismus. 4aVideospiele. 7aHISTORY / Study & Teaching.2bisacsh  aCollective memory.  aFirst World War.  aHistorical memory.  aRacism.  aVideo Games.0 cEPUBz97831107293680 cprintz978311072984940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311072930640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110729306423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110729306/original  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK